com.project.fipu

Class ParseFIPU_Two

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.project.fipu.ParseFIPU_Two

  • public class ParseFIPU_Two
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the exclusive parsing task for the first FIPU. This parsing class is only working for the webservice provided by the API : api.flightstats.com.
    Author:
    Group Sascha Scatà, Jan Raphael Schmid Niederkofler, Christine Lunger, Benjamin Egger
